headline: Tyson Foods (TSN) Stock Trades Up, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of meat company Tyson Foods (NYSE:TSN) jumped 3.1% in the afternoon session after investors reacted positively to the company's recent move to streamline its beef operations for better long-term efficiency.
